@startuml uml_class_analytics
title LLD — analytics-service (gRPC + Kafka — proto/analytics.proto)
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica

package "HTTP / gRPC transport" {
  class "Ingest / query HTTP\n(server.ts)" as Http <<Node>>
  class "AnalyticsService\n(grpc-server.ts)" as Grpc <<Node>> {
    GetDailyMetrics()
    GetRecommendations()
    GetWatchlistInsights()
    AnalyzeListingFeel()
  }
  class "RecommendationAdminService\n(internal RPC)" as Admin <<Node>> {
    ActivateModel()
    SetExperimentTraffic()
  }
}

package "Application" {
  class "Projection builder\n/ rollups" as P <<service>>
}

package "Infrastructure" {
  class "Facts & metrics\n(Postgres)" as R <<repository>>
  class "Kafka consumer\n(domain events)" as C
}

C --> P
Http --> P
Grpc --> P
Admin --> P
P --> R

note bottom of Grpc
  **Contract:** `proto/analytics.proto`
  — read-oriented queries; **never**
  mutates other services' source DBs.
  Admin service for model/experiment
  control plane only.
end note

@enduml
